hletes\", \"from\": 4043, \"to\": 4062}, {\"ngram\": \"stigma\", \"from\": 4078, \"to\": 4084}, {\"ngram\": \"attitudes\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4101}, {\"ngram\": \"the limits\", \"from\": 4116, \"to\": 4126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The problem is these two weeks can be too quickly be forgotten, especially by politicians - from more than just one nation - who laud their athletes' achievements one day and then cut their allowances the next.\", \"from\": 4169, \"to\": 4379, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The problem\", \"from\": 4169, \"to\": 4180}, {\"ngram\": \"these two weeks\", \"from\": 4184, \"to\": 4199}, {\"ngram\": \"politicians\", \"from\": 4247, \"to\": 4258}, {\"ngram\": \"just one nation\", \"from\": 4276, \"to\": 4291}, {\"ngram\": \"their athletes' achievements\", \"from\": 4303, \"to\": 4331}, {\"ngram\": \"their allowances\", \"from\": 4353, \"to\": 4369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the International Paralympic Committee, people with disabilities make up about 15 per cent of the global population, the largest marginalised group in the world.\", \"from\": 4381, \"to\": 4555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4398, \"end\": 4432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Paralympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4440}, {\"ngram\": \"disabilities\", \"from\": 4446, \"to\": 4458}, {\"ngram\": \"about 15 per cent\", \"from\": 4467, \"to\": 4484}, {\"ngram\": \"the global population\", \"from\": 4488, \"to\": 4509}, {\"ngram\": \"the largest marginalised group\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4541}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 4545, \"to\": 4554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is also - according to the Wor